title: Ruckus Spot Access Points
agents: ruckus
catalog: app/ruckus
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check outputs information of the access points for the 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz bands
 taken from the Ruckus Spot web interface. It shows the number of total devices
 and the amount of access points with time drift and not responding problems.
 For each problem type you can configure warn and crit levels.

inventory:
 Creates one check.

